description:
Kangaroos has been a real sneaker brand from the start. The brand was founded in America in 1979 when the architect Bob Gamm, who loved jogging, wondered where to keep his key while jogging. The solution was a self-designed jogging shoe that had a small, sealed pocket at the front. He called the shoes Kangaroos and used Dynacoil ™, a technology discovered and designed by NASA. In a few years time, the trendy jogging shoes with pocket became a success in many countries. The unique pouch can still be found on every model. All Kangaroos sneakers are characterized by the unique design in combination with functionality and high quality.
StyleCode: 472779046
title: Finalist " Vibram"
